<div class="entryuserpic"><img src="http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/35861700/1334450" title="" alt=""height="100" width="100"  /></div></div>

<div class="entrycontent">Oh, and currently less than 1% of the MBTA is financed with advertising (look <a href="http://mbta.com/uploadedFiles/Documents/Financials/SORE_History.pdf">here</a> for a simple funding breakdown).  Note that state taxes provide ~55% of the income and local taxes provide ~10%.  Another interesting tidbit is that 17% of the money spent was interest and 8% was principal payments on loans.</div>

